section.text:

Section 550(b) of the Department of Homeland Security Appropriations Act, 2007 (Public Law 109–295; 
  6 U.S.C. 121 note), as amended by 
section 537 of the Department of Homeland Security Appropriations Act, 2013 (Public Law 113–6), is further amended by striking on October 4, 2013 and inserting on October 4, 2014.

From the unobligated balances made available in the Department of the Treasury Forfeiture Fund established by 
            section 9703 of title 31, United States Code, (added by section 638 of Public Law 102–393
          ) $100,000,000 shall be permanently rescinded.
